trans-unit.source: A ComponentRenameEventArgs provides data about a <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IComponentChangeService.ComponentRename> event.
trans-unit.target: Um ComponentRenameEventArgs fornece dados sobre um <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IComponentChangeService.ComponentRename>evento.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IComponentChangeService.ComponentRename>

trans-unit.source: A ComponentRenameEventArgs object provides the following information: - A <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentRenameEventArgs.Component%2A> property that references the component being renamed.
trans-unit.target: Um objeto ComponentRenameEventArgs fornece as seguintes informações: - um <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentRenameEventArgs.Component%2A>propriedade que referencia o componente que está sendo renomeado.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentRenameEventArgs.Component%2A>

trans-unit.source: - An <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentRenameEventArgs.OldName%2A> property that indicates the old name of the component.
trans-unit.target: -Um <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentRenameEventArgs.OldName%2A>propriedade que indica o nome antigo do componente.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentRenameEventArgs.OldName%2A>

trans-unit.source: - A <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentRenameEventArgs.NewName%2A> property that indicates the new name of the component.
trans-unit.target: -A <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentRenameEventArgs.NewName%2A>propriedade que indica o novo nome do componente.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentRenameEventArgs.NewName%2A>
